            . On the 26th of June I was in <placeName id="t18320705-231-crimeloc1213">Ball-alley, Shoreditch</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18320705-231-crimeloc1213" type="placeName" value="Ball-alley, Shoreditch"></interp>
